reviewText: Mr. Trejo's lifelong commitment to learning and teaching, is shown with impeccable balance, movement, and power.  It is easy to see why Kenpo Karate students, have been the majority winners of tournaments in years past.
The DVD, "ABC's of Kenpo Karate Vol. 1" is very instructional. Frank Trejo is a great martial artist and instructor of kenpo karate. Jerry Chilton
